	* CitcomS/Controller.py, CitcomS/Solver/Solver.py,
	  module/Regional/bindings.cc, module/Regional/misc.cc,
	  module/Regional/misc.h: A quick fix to issue35 "inconsistent
	  times in C and Pyre"

